extendedInfo.description: You loved the 24 TV series. You loved Jack Bauer. Your going to love the 24 movie. You know he could kick Walker Texas Ranger blindfolded, no matter what Walker's fans think.This is the application for you.Hundreds of Jack Bauer quotes, jokes and facts for fun and profit. We hope you like it.This is the FREE version of the app that displays an ad screen every few facts displayed. A pay-for application will be available too.For feedback, complaints, suggestions, ideas or just to say hi, email us at support@cosmyc.com. Thanks!

reviews.title: Very nice
reviews.comment: 24 is my all time favourite series...this app was fun to read....who ever made this has good sense of humour....but you should know ,no one makes fun of Jack Bauer
reviews.author: A Google User
